Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一邊去 我要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鳩 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有什麼我能幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(兼職 招聘信息)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊

Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:15.99,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:11.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:11.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:30.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:30.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:42.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:42.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:16.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:16.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

