Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...偵探 花戶小鳩.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來兼職有這麼多種類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種書借來幹什麼...啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要兼職啦 像籐本先生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幫忙還一點借款麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在清爽的早晨送報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是睡懶覺的你去送?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如為大家送披薩到家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那...那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如幫忙搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬運瓶瓶罐罐的時候大概會搞砸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚 那要兼怎樣的職才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 縫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有一件事想拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 借傘的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那個時候的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前承蒙照顧 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你們認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 自我介紹一下 我是店長植田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩小姐是在我的公寓裡住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時在艾草保育園幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想找個可以兼職的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想起這家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果週末店裡很忙的時候能來幫忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的手治好為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是這種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我其實很冒失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是前兩天弄傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過忙起來的時候 店長太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 也請您多關照 店長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫大村裕美 請多關照 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼加油吧 小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 太好了 制服很合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先客人來了的話 要說"歡迎光臨"歡迎光臨!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就...就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後問客人要買什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問好把蛋糕裝進那個盒子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收銀機我來操作 收錢以後...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說"謝謝惠顧"是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 先試一試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我要草莓蛋糕和勃朗峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士蛋糕...不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕 勃朗峰 奶酪...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果?檸檬?呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要奶油泡芙 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕和勃朗峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果派加檸檬派和奶油泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 把它們裝進盒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...草莓蛋糕和... 哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定一點 另取一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是勃朗峰和...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果派和檸檬派 奶油泡芙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 最後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 活潑的店員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 習慣了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿裡奈和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩是蛋糕店員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天是蛋糕店員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什麼蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們來取滿裡奈的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天你生日啊 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 幫她裝起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(滿裡奈 生日快樂)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿錯蛋糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?我去追滿裡奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿裡奈!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我那個和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 這位客人是要勃朗峰和芝士蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表是個布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?明天再來也可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美你也可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 整理工作還沒有做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷還沒有好 不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼店長我先回...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?沒...沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看上去裕美小姐好像在擔心著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長有點讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像有什麼煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然問過他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻說"沒什麼"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的生意也有條不紊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼店長是為什麼煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是欠債?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育園正為這個焦頭爛額呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩難道是為此才在這裡兼職的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...我不算什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師和籐本先生才了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想要是能夠出上一點力就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想出點力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為店長...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幫忙卻幫不上忙的話是很痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去調查看看店長的煩惱到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要做多餘的事情然後被炒魷魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這麼好吃的蛋糕就吃不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是還可以去其他各種地方打工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級中華料理店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩...接下來打算在哪裡打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還是繼續去蛋糕店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我把這些曲奇放到貨架上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 店長是不是對我歎了一口氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道店長所煩惱的事 與我有關?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去問問店長到底有什麼煩心事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼能不能若無其事地幫我問問?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 小鳩加油了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有事要若無其事地問問您!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長是不是有什麼煩惱的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 什麼事情都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 裕美小姐說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您經常若有所思地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼話欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實裕美不用擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一說更覺得放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩會在這裡幫忙一直到我的傷痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您來買蛋糕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去千歲家玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帶些手信去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久違了呢 chiroru的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得您曾經為您丈夫訂過生日蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師的丈夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說結婚了有老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從來沒有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可能離婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師看上去很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事 可不能直接問哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有不想說的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不都瞞著大家為了保育園去打工的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都一樣 並不是什麼都該說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru的店長也是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裕美小姐很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候到底要怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 比如悄悄地調查之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可不認為這是土鳩能勝任的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還算得上是悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在悄悄地調查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像偵探一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來這就是偵探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要調查很多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動機啊 不在場證明 證據之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有搜查啊 聽取證言 跟蹤什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥 我們也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 偵探是獨自行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像偏離方向了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我今天是偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru裡有沒有什麼不正常的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 沒有吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是不是發生了什麼事件..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是店長煩惱事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煩惱?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼線索呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算你問我們也...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru的蛋糕很有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是工作以外的事情吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那我們就先走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要陪你玩這種遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我自己的搜查網
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查網?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能接受那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小氣啊 玄琥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要商量戀愛方面的事 你還是找別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就這樣把手信帶回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你只是想過來白吃年輪蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今知道的只有chiroru的蛋糕很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以煩惱的原因在工作以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是店長他總是送小孩子巧克力做贈品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會注意別人的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了大家都很喜歡店長做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也收到巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長對大家都很友善呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐 現在開始要跟蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 算了吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和誰有約嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷跟在後邊是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是約會?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會不對我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被店長發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 剛剛和店長見面的那位是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是面試...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備新收的兼職的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職?為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然週末小鳩會來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直不能讓裕美你好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你會不會是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 會受傷是不是也因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是在煩惱這件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美真的做的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則是太依賴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 我和店長一起工作覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有休假也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天接觸那些因為蛋糕而高興的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有和店長一起讓我覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受傷是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是裕美...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傷是在練習做蛋糕的時候弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想哪怕能多幫店長一點也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就學著...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞞著你真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能吃吃看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且新的兼職的人也要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的時候一起學習做蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛解決掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小鳩偵探解決掉事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長是因為想讓裕美休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而裕美則是想能更好地幫助店長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都在為對方著想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣一個美好的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又吃到年輪蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蛋糕不是chiroru的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且以前也作為手信帶回來過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:22:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道和五百祗先生的搜查網有什麼關係哦 對了 這次的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吃到了蛋糕所以滿分一百分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是手信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我兼職的店裡的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以籐本先生就多點休息 多點去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就算你努力也沒什麼用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺負人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強了把自己弄病了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是在擔心我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個還是去把臉上的塗鴉弄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是一百分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼的 那是塗鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 籐本先生太欺負人了只給五十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你說啥...

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...銀色之瞳.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
